&lt;li&gt;Lead day-to-day operations of the practice with a proactive mindset, addressing workflow opportunities, resolving issues before they affect patients or staff, and improving operational efficiency across all functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively manage and optimize provider schedules to maximize clinical capacity, reduce gaps, and support practice growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion a culture of exceptional patient experience, addressing concerns promptly and thoroughly, implementing root-cause corrective actions, and monitoring and reacting to satisfaction metrics to drive continuous service improvement&lt;/li&gt;
