&lt;li&gt;Skill in using healthcare software and computer systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of maintaining supplies and equipment for the medical setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multitasking and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
